Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實身份很快就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬同學 你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 就算你是警視總監的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能每次都到現場來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中森警部 至今為止你都是怎麼辦案的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場可是留下了直接而重要的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是頭髮 怪盜基德的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要查出基德的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能接近蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經結束歐洲巡演 應該馬上會潛入日本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬偵探 基德又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請發表一下感想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這是要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知道了 警部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法球 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上最美的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅子大人您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的男人都是您的俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只有怪盜基德例外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽快斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到何時才會成為我的俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您冷靜點 就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 他還是會成為我的俘虜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您會使用魔法 也是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他不久就會從你眼前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 您瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是… 轉學生白馬探
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這建築還真夠壯觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我叔父的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您請看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是至今為止我收集到的基德資料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盜基德 身高174CM 體重50KG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視力左眼2.0 右眼2.0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音無數 體育全能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中力驚人 卻缺乏毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 性格也很差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿探少爺 頭髮檢測完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑髮 日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血型B
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測年齡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總歸是三十大幾 四十幾歲唄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 說不定可能50多歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測年齡為15到17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 還是個高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是從20多歲就開始追捕他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基德預告了明晚也要動手 忙得要死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺 這當中恐怕出了差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過這裡各種資料應有盡有是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 收集了各類領域的獨家調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想借用高中生的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本所有高中生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要熬夜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓捕基德失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬名偵探也遭遇連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐你了 無能偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快斗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青子你幹嘛 一大早鬼叫什麼 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你呼呼大睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節課都已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡太多小心變成傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著幹了幾天活 快累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很累的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬同學會遲到真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去很疲倦呢 名偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 次次都讓基德逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是會身心俱疲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊 好討厭的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可精神的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直都在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基德連續預告的最後地點 大島美術館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想邀你今晚同去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你有什麼理由不方便去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 該不會是知道我的身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 正好還方便我幹活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去就去唄 讓我見識一下你的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家要把基德抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽同學 還是別去為好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 紅子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果 果然是個美人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅子同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的資料不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人說會兒話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許對紅子動歪腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 圈套？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是白馬同學為了抓你設的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非要抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想裝傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是怪盜基德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會罷手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕明知是個圈套 我也必須面對挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真是怪盜基德的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好學習 天天向上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你被人抓住算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從我眼前消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的男人就都是我的俘虜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果他真的消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法球 請讓我再看清楚些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 白馬探會給基德設下怎樣的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可 紅子小姐 你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡會發生非常恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界最大的粉色藍寶石？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據美術館方面介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是收藏家J?P?塔納的藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說 他還是英國有名的雕刻家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他非常講究 每件寶石的展示都精心設計過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡都有怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我們很難辦事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝置已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧 基德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨什麼嗨 青子 你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連快斗也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白馬同學邀請我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 青子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬同學 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是在開派對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓令愛一睹逮捕基德的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼掉以輕心 小心追悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 萬萬不可掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他已經潛入進來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的樣子 果然和在學校時完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有偵探的范兒 真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 青子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡太危險 到二樓去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子 得意忘形什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快斗也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憋死了 憋死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說順利潛入了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還得抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多要變裝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經什麼都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨晚基德掉落在現場的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經查明他是個高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在將全國高中生的資訊和基德進行比對後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個名字浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的名字 黑羽快斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了基德預告的時間 就能見分曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 離預告時間還差1分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間都浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 放馬過來 基德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 根本沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是快坦白真實身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盜基德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照預告 寶石我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃 掃帚？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 你還有閒心佩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘娘腔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基德 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個讓人操心的基德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基德…該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面 別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 來玩個小遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到你的噩夢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這是你的噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你引向毀滅的噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 紅子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅…子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇高的友情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 只要你是如假包換的基德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底何為真相 何為謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷 現在你就是基德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為黑羽盜一已經不在這個世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 是這傢伙把老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又叫君特?馮?高德柏格二世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上是世界級的幻術師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 這個名字也並非真名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本名不詳 國籍不詳 年齡不詳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定會揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會吧 基德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了 噩夢時刻伴隨著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 好險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然中了幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子我就不欠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛 你休想搶走基德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是你 白馬 還是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為黑羽快斗註定會是我的俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白馬同學 基德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 這個掛在那棵樹上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 怪盜基德是不是有兩個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才騎在掃帚上 是個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盜基德是…
